59010::$$$message_0529_0000_0000$$$::The lead actor exits the stage,[lr]::
59011::$$$message_0529_0000_0001$$$::leaving only a wordless corpse.[lr]::
59012::$$$message_0529_0000_0002$$$::And something[lr]::
59013::$$$message_0529_0000_0003$$$::consumes it.[lr]::
59014::$$$message_0529_0000_0004$$$::It leaves no body.[lr]::
59015::$$$message_0529_0000_0005$$$::The wooden floor becomes a bottomless swamp, its crimson mass spreading out to consume the man's unmoving body.::
59016::$$$message_0529_0001_0000$$$::It takes not only the man, but the thing he used to command.[lr]::
59017::$$$message_0529_0001_0001$$$::The soul modeled after the Servant Caster falls to the black shadow.[lr]::
59018::$$$message_0529_0001_0002$$$::That is not how things should be.[lr]::
59019::$$$message_0529_0001_0003$$$::When a Servant loses and disappears, it goes back to the Holy Grail.[lr]::
59020::$$$message_0529_0001_0004$$$::Something which violates this rule is subject to inevitable decay, no matter how powerful it is.::
59021::$$$message_0529_0002_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
59022::$$$message_0529_0002_0001$$$::It cries without a sound.[lr]::
59023::$$$message_0529_0002_0002$$$::In anguish, it bubbles and churns until it finally devours the first person.::
59024::$$$message_0529_0003_0000$$$::    NOT ENOUGH::
59025::$$$message_0529_0004_0000$$$::It shuffles forward, like waves lapping on the shore.[lr]::
59026::$$$message_0529_0004_0001$$$::It has no voice to scream, so it expresses pain with its entire body.::
59027::$$$message_0529_0005_0000$$$::    NOT ENOUGH::
59028::$$$message_0529_0006_0000$$$::It has no words, no emotions.[lr]::
59029::$$$message_0529_0006_0001$$$::From the beginning, it was never equipped with such functions.::
59030::$$$message_0529_0007_0000$$$::    NOT ENOUGH::
59031::$$$message_0529_0008_0000$$$::And yet, it grieves.[lr]::
59032::$$$message_0529_0008_0001$$$::It laments its very being,[lr]::
59033::$$$message_0529_0008_0002$$$::like something that has become aware of its own existence for the first time.=nè`